description:
Just in time for Halloween, or maybe you are re-thinking your Christmas themes? "The Spookies" set of 5 digital downloadable designs. Includes Spookie Witchie, Darla, Igor, Edgar, and Spider.

Image is black and grey, may be printed on a color or black and white printer on 8 1/2 x 11" paper. You get one design in two sizes, two directions. 

Digital Download PDF document. 6 pages, 8 1/2” x 11” 300 dpi.
A link to your digital download will be sent to your email address.

You are not allowed to use for commercial purposes. You may not share, transfer, or redistribute the images. This is for your personal use only. Camille Rose Garcia maintains copyrights to all images, copyright is not transfered with purchase.

name: Winchester Hoot Doll: Huckleberry Edition. Jumbo size
description:
Winchester Hoot owl printed on cotton/linen fabric with a wool felt backing. Jumbo Winchester Hoot is 15”h x 6.5”w x 2.5”d.  Filled with polyester/hemp/wool blend with a lavender and cedar aromatic insert. Felt and sequin bow detail at neck with a hanging fabric name-tag, “Greetings, my name is Winchester Hoot”.  Monacle sequin detail on right eye.
 Ships with mini info-booklet with story insert. Made entirely in the USA with mostly natural materials, designed to last. Packaged in a clear plastic protective sleeve. WARNING: Small parts!! Not intended for small children or babies.

name: Odd-Occassion Greeting card set
description: Did you forget your cat's birthday? Maybe you need to thank your pal for chasing away night-ghosts. Well whatever the occasion, it sure is nice to have some of these on hand when you need them! You get 2 of each design: "Sorry", "Darling", and "Thank You", plus 6 white envelopes. Each card is 5" x 7",  printed on heavy-weight matte paper with a blank interior. They come in a nice clear box with a backing card, ready for gifting if you are so inclined. Hey, you could even send one to me to thank me for making them.
